        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Double Chocolate Peppermint Cookies. An American family-table recipe — generous, comforting, built for a crowd. Adjustable for what you need."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Cookies bake fast and reward a chilled dough. Pull them out when the edges set and the middles still look slightly underdone."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
